show.description: Blessy was betrayed by her sister, spent one night with a stranger, and gave birth to two kids. But when her sister finds out that the father of those kids was so rich and handsome, she abducted one kid without Blessy knowing. years after when Blessy finds truth, what will she do? Watch Now!
